r foreign workers i.e. visas, work permits etc.\n3.\tManage fulfilment of all bylaw requirements for foreign students\n4.\tDesign and maintain administrative systems that deliver outcomes based on the school’s aims and goals \n5.\tHire and terminate workers as necessary\n6.\tDirect and coordinate activities of the entire business and/or departments concerned with the production, pricing, sales, and/or distribution of products.\n7.\tDetermine (along with the Board) the Annual Strategic goals and company Budget\n8.\tMonitor the business and agencies to ensure that they efficiently and effectively provide needed services while staying within budgetary limits\n9.\tDevelop and implement product marketing strategies including advertising campaign, sales promotions, and all social media platforms \n10.\tPlan and direct activities such as sales promotions, coordinating with other department heads as required\n11.\tContribute to team effort by accomplishing related results as needed\n12.\tAssure that the school reaches the standards, as determined by the Ministry of Education", "experiences/0/jobLocation": "Bangkok City, Thailand", "experiences/0/jobStartedOn": "10-2017", "experiences/0/jobStillWorking": "true", "experiences/0/title": "General Manager", "experiences/1/companyName": "Bangkok Thai Cooking Academy", "experiences/1/employmentType": "Full-time", "experiences/1/jobDescription": "- Looking for chefs to match with restaurants and hotels required\n- Arrange interviews and cooking test\n- Communicate with clients who looking for chefs\n- Preparing documents for chefs to get the working visa", "experiences/1/jobLocation": "Bangkok, Bangkok City, Thailand", "experiences/1/jobStartedOn": "1-2016", "experiences/1/jobStillWorking": "true", "experiences/1/title": "Chefs Placement Specialist", "experiences/2/companyId": "28849225", "experiences/2/companyIndustry": "Professional Training and Coaching", "experiences/2/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/thai-chef-school/", "experiences/2/companyName": "Thai Chef School", "experiences/2/companySize": "51-200", "experiences/2/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:28849225", "experiences/2/companyWebsite": "https://thaichefschool.com/", "experiences/2/employmentType": "Full-time", "experiences/2/jobDescription": "Responsibilities: \n1.\tManage the whole school administrative function and lead all support staff\n2.\tManage necessarily as needed by laws for foreigners’ workers e.g. visa and work permit\n3.\tManage necessarily as needed by laws for foreigners’ students\n4.\tDesign and maintain administrative systems that deliver outcomes based on the school’s aims and goals \n5.\tHire and terminate workers as needed\n6.\tDirect and coordinate activities of businesses or departments concerned with the production, pricing, sales, and/or distribution of products.\n7.\tMonitor businesses and agencies to ensure that they efficiently and effectively provide needed services while staying within budgetary limits\n8.\tDevelop and implement product marketing strategies including advertising campaigns and sales promotions\n9.\tPlan and direct activities such as sales promotions, coordinating with other department heads as required\n10.\tContributes to team effort by accomplishing related results as needed\n11.\tAssure the school to reach the standard as the Ministry of Education determine", "experiences/2/jobEndedOn": "10-2020", "experiences/2/jobLocation": "Bangkok City, Thailand", "experiences/2/jobLocationCountry": "TH", "experiences/2/jobStartedOn": "10-2017", "experiences/2/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/2/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C560BAQFqVplGq8DvYg/company-logo_400_400/company-logo_400_400/0/1630602214968?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=z32g25V-QEYEQBLgpgj5xwNBC0riP6TosupAcaRbAVY", "experiences/2/title": "General Manager", "experiences/3/companyName": "Walen Education Co.,Ltd.", "experiences/3/jobDescription": "•\tManagement\n-\tTraining new staff\n-\tArranging the incom