00&v=beta&t=ZKeXCKXgvrAOVoHjFadnKy-jLxHSrj8llNLJQVcTBE4", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/public_identifier": "prasert-choomtong-19302698", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/url": "https://linkedin.com/in/ACoAABSmC38BS3OsST4wftEGg1YENB9KAI3La38", "profilePic": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C5603AQFQcyTTwvbx2g/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/0/1624075159024?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=0wN7q3EAUpsVfwSIFZJERQ4kIeDj_PCMjfO9uIJDbmg", "profilePicHighQuality": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C5603AQFQcyTTwvbx2g/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/0/1624075159024?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=0wN7q3EAUpsVfwSIFZJERQ4kIeDj_PCMjfO9uIJDbmg", "publicIdentifier": "bart-callens-868b792", "recommendations/0/context": "Bart was senior to Lucas but didn't manage Lucas directly", "recommendations/0/date": "August 30, 2021", "recommendations/0/description": "I had the pleasure to work with Lucas during my tenure as Area General Manager for IHG Southern Thailand Resorts while he was General Manager at the Holiday Inn Resort Phi Phi. Lucas showed great acumen in understanding resort operations, brand management, sales, revenue management, finance, HR and team leadership. He managed to keep this resort at the forefront on Phi Phi island when it came to guest satisfaction & profitability. His relationship with his team, owners and peers was exceptional and he always conducted himself with utmost professionalism. I have no hesitation to recommend Lucas to any potential employer and wish him the very best in his future endeavors. ", "recommendations/0/name": "Lucas Chanter", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "General Manager & Director of Operations | Luxury Resorts · Multi-Property Portfolios · P&L to USD $25M | SE Asia · Pacific · Caribbean | Open to GM, Group GM & COO Roles", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/lucaschanter/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAD_mlsBnr1ykSSOI6NZIcrDM9vYr5kcAhg", "recommendations/1/context": "Bart reported directly to Elf", "recommendations/1/date": "August 19, 2021", "recommendations/1/description": "I had the pleasure to work for Elf Seah who represented my owning company during my tenure at the Holiday Inn Resort Phuket from 2016 to 2020. I immensely enjoyed working with him and I learned a lot from him on general asset management. Furthermore, he gave a lot of 'space' to me as an operator to run the property and to lead the team throughout the stormy waters we had during the 2020-2021 pandemic. On a personal basis, Elf has always been very engaging, proactive and approachable when needed. I would recommend Elf to any employer and I would be very pleased to work for & with him again in the future. ", "recommendations/1/name": "Elf Seah", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Portfolio Manager, Global Infrastructure at Google", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/elfseah/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAALJR8QBuDEP5mlHDrdncuzAFZ6ybsS52q8", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Bjorn worked with Bart on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "June 30, 2021", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "I enjoy working closely with Bart ever since 2018, including the challenging Covid19 situation. Bart is an engaged, proactive, innovative and honest leader who naturally gains the trust of his team and local community to help him drive the business forward in a responsible and sustainable way. Without a doubt I look forward to continue to work closely with Bart going forward in one way or another.", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Bjorn Courage", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "President | Phuket Hotels Association | General Manager | InterContinental Phuket Resort | Driving Premium Tourism Strategy in Southeast Asia", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/bjorn-courage-9582a4/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAAK4lQBkJFwjfhl-cKlF0i2sCdTxputD50", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Lucas reported directly to Bart", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "June 24, 2021", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "I worked with Bart during my time as GM of Holiday Inn Phi Phi Island. Bart was both a mentor and friend throughout the 3+ years we worked together. He was always there when needed and really held the IHG Southern team together leading by example with the utmost professionalism. He is respected and admired by both his own team and peers in Phuket due to his committed leadership and continual dedication to tourism in the region.", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Lucas Chanter", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "General Manager & Director of Operations | Luxury Resorts · Multi-Property Portfolios · P&L to USD $25M | SE Asia · Pacific · Caribbean | Open to GM, Group GM & COO Roles", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/lucaschanter/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAD_mlsBnr1ykSSOI6NZIcrDM9vYr5kcAhg", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Elf managed Bart directly", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "June 21, 2021", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "I was the Asset Manager from the owning company of the Holiday Inn Resort Phuket where Bart was the General Manager since 2016.  Bart steered the 34-year old Hotel through many challenges, not least the COVID-19 pandemic. His strong leadership was instrumental to resolving many of the numerous legacy challenges and kept the Hotel on the apex amongst the many hotels in Patong. I definitely appreciated his straight and no-nonsense communicative style and I know I can count on him to always deliver the truth - good or bad.  Bart's experience and leadership will absolutely be an asset to any hotel or portfolio and I am will not hesitate to recommend him should a reference is required. ", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Elf Seah", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Portfolio Manager, Global Infrastructure at Google", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/elfseah/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAALJR8QBuDEP5mlHDrdncuzAFZ6ybsS52q8", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Michel managed Bart directly", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "March 10, 2013", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "Bart was my resident manager at the Crowne plaza West Hanoi and reported directly to me. During that time we faced a very challenging business environment and had to position a new property in an emerging area of Hanoi. Bart was a very important player in the team, he proved to be incredibly helpful and knowledgeable. These qualities combined with his integrity and trustworthiness and dedication to achieve key objectives were extremely important to the success of the hotel in key areas.\nI recommend Bart with no hesitation.", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Michel Chertouh", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "Luxury Hospitality Leader | Managing Director at Regent Hong Kong", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/michel-chertouh-901408/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAAPaxEBeTzLsemqRqlP39NS20t3LOw1TdM", "recommendationsReceived/4/context": "Daniel P. worked with Bart on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "January 14, 2013", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "Bart's talents lies in his great understanding of all important hotel operation areas, brand management & marketing, sales functions, revenue management, finance, human resources and team leadership. With his dedication the property managed to become the leading Crowne Plaza brand hotel in South East Asia measured on guest satisfaction. His leadership is well balanced with the right drive to deliver owners and company revenue expectations. He is without any doubt a great talent with his rich expertise in the industry and I am sure to see him shortly in a General Manager position. I can highly recommend his talent and I am privileged to work with him to continue our success.", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "Daniel P. Kipping", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "VP Commercial || Director Of Operations || Sales & Commercial Specialist || Business Mentor || Hotel Business Optimizer || Startup’er", "recommendationsReceived/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/dkipping/", "recommendationsReceived/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAFUAs4Bv_l9ANUeUDpqYPVkZlsFydWKNVA", "recommendationsReceived/5/context": "Frederic managed Bart directly", "recommendationsReceived/5/date": "August 15, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/5/description": "Bart was part of the pre opening team, in a very challenging environment Bart managed to position the food and beverage department as a destination in the region. Bart has demonstrate a very strong acumen in finance furthermore he has initiated new concept and develop the sales accordingly. Bart is a strong person when it comes to move project forward and he is also a very reliable person.", "recommendationsReceived/5/name": "Frederic Picard", "recommendationsReceived/5/subtitle": "World bank group, IFC, board member, CEO, hospitality, tourism, education, hotel development, transition management, La Réserve Paris, Oetker collection, Maisons Pariente.", "recommendationsReceived/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/frederic-picard-15250a2/", "recommendationsReceived/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABuYE4BJ-FebMEd8wsTJ1piVxtEQljR22U", "recommendationsReceived/6/context": "Patrick worked with Bart on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/6/date": "April 28, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/6/description": "Bart is a very professional colleague,fully efficient on planification and orgasization and totally customer oriented.\nHis strong f&b background lead him to take responsability in divers segments of hospitality opération with success.\nI will be very pleased to work with him again!", "recommendationsReceive