1, 2015", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "Pam joined The Stones initially on task force basis and did so well that we asked her to stay on. She knows her business inside out, creates meaningful relationships with both her associates and customers and is an highly effective team member. Pam's enthusiasm, passion, analytical sense and dynamic approach were things I always appreciated. ", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Theo Ocks", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Nothing happens until someone sells something!", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/theoocks/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAASwSMBsfZq167UCgfNqcrDF4EXAtlUdJ0", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Jimmy managed Pamela directly", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "November 12, 2013", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "I have only two words for those who are looking for a hardworking , dedicated and efficient Director of Sales and Marketing - Hire Her !\nJimmy Yeo", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Jimmy Yeo", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "ApexKey Hotel , Resort & Condominium Management Consultant", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/jimmy-yeo-a5089013/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAALMrtwBch_G1YEMtZCA8BxSQ_eps0EQoVQ", "recommendationsReceived/4/context": "Marcel managed Pamela directly", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "November 12, 2013", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "Pamela demonstrated on a consistent basis that she's is a quick learner and a that she's a Manager who stays very engaged with her team and with her customers. She's innovative, very result driven and always willing to go the extra mile.", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "Marcel Hinderer", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "General Manager at Hotel Villa Honegg", "recommendationsReceived/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/marcel-hinderer-15464a28/", "recommendationsReceived